3509	  At the presheaf level the pullback--pushforward adjunction unit at the monoidal unit,
3510	  post-composed with the pushforward of the oplax unit comparison, recovers the lax unit:
3511	  \[
3512	    \mathtt{presheafAdj}.\mathrm{unit}.\mathrm{app}\,\mathbf{1}^{\mathrm{p}}
3513	      \;\mathbin{;}\;
3514	      (\mathtt{pushforward}\,\varphi').\mathrm{map}\,(\eta\,F)
3515	      \;=\; \varepsilon(\mathtt{pushforward}\,\varphi'),
3516	  \]
3517	  where \(\mathtt{presheafAdj} = \mathtt{pullbackPushforwardAdjunction}\,\varphi'\) is the
3518	  presheaf pullback--pushforward adjunction and \(F = \mathtt{pullback}\,\varphi'\).
3519	\end{lemma}
