3525	  pullback--pushforward adjunction \(\mathtt{pullbackPushforwardAdjunction}\,\varphi'\). That
3526	  identity holds for any adjunction whose left adjoint is oplax monoidal and whose right adjoint
3527	  is lax monoidal in a mate-compatible way. The compatible pair is
3528	  \(\mathtt{presheafPushforwardLaxMonoidal}\)
3529	  (\cref{lem:presheaf_pushforward_laxmonoidal}) and \(\mathtt{presheafPullbackOplaxMonoidal}\)
3530	  (\cref{lem:presheaf_pullback_oplaxmonoidal}), so the
