3542	      a_Y.\mathrm{map}\,(\eta\,F) \;\mathbin{;}\;
3543	      \mathtt{sheafifyUnitIso}.\mathrm{hom}
3544	      \;=\; \mathtt{pullbackObjUnitToUnit}\,\varphi
3545	  \]
3546	  commutes. Then \(a_Y.\mathrm{map}\,(\eta\,F)\) is an isomorphism.
3547	\end{lemma}
